705
00:22:53,400 --> 00:22:55,420
 oni su to govorili u Saboru.

706
00:22:55,420 --> 00:22:55,680
 Dakle,

707
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,120
 imate nas koji smo se borili

708
00:22:57,120 --> 00:22:57,760
 za slobodu,

709
00:22:57,760 --> 00:22:58,940
 njih koji su nam tu slobodu

710
00:22:58,940 --> 00:22:59,740
 htjeli otimati,

711
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:00,660
 a danas,

712
00:23:00,660 --> 00:23:01,840
 iz naše perspektive,

713
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:02,140
 dakle,

714
00:23:02,140 --> 00:23:03,940
 stvarno ne prestaju udarati

715
00:23:03,940 --> 00:23:04,580
 na te temelje.

716
00:23:04,580 --> 00:23:05,260
 Pazite ovo,

717
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:06,120
 zamislite ovako,

718
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:07,060
 da se,

719
00:23:07,060 --> 00:23:07,380
 ne,

720
00:23:07,380 --> 00:23:08,540
 nisu ni trebali svi,

721
00:23:08,540 --> 00:23:09,260
 da se dvoje,

722
00:23:09,260 --> 00:23:11,280
 troje ljevih zastupnika

723
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:12,280
 pojavili u Kninu.

724
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:14,000
 Oni bi bili spremni

725
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:14,780
 možda pretrpiti

726
00:23:14,780 --> 00:23:15,740
 neke zvižduke i sve,

727
00:23:15,740 --> 00:23:16,700
 ali ne smijemo biti

728
00:23:16,700 --> 00:23:17,200
 pa huljice.

729
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:17,480
 Dakle,

730
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:18,800
 mi koji se bavimo javni poslo,

731
00:23:18,800 --> 00:23:20,380
 moraš biti spremni na udarci

732
00:23:20,380 --> 00:23:21,320
 ili ide sad i paprike

733
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:22,640
 i baviti se nečim drugim u životu.

734
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:23,940
 Da su došli u Knin,

735
00:23:23,940 --> 00:23:26,260
 da dođu baš osamnaistoga

736
00:23:26,260 --> 00:23:27,140
 u Vukovar,

737
00:23:27,140 --> 00:23:27,640
 studenog,

738
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:28,680
 ne dan prije pa bacaju

739
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:30,360
 za poginule,

740
00:23:30,360 --> 00:23:30,800
 dakle,

741
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:32,180
 srpske civile,

742
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:33,380
 nego za hrvatske branitelje

743
00:23:33,380 --> 00:23:34,480
 koji su branili Vukovar

744
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:35,220
 koji je uništen

745
00:23:35,220 --> 00:23:36,780
 pod okupacijom Četnjika JNA,

746
00:23:36,780 --> 00:23:38,860
 da oni na takav način,

747
00:23:38,860 --> 00:23:40,060
 da su došli na Jazovku

748
00:23:40,060 --> 00:23:40,880
 i rekli,

749
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:41,900
 mi smo pripadnici

750
00:23:41,900 --> 00:23:43,260
 ljevih političnih priča,

751
00:23:43,260 --> 00:23:44,240
 mi duboko vjerujemo

752
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:44,760
 u tu naši,

753
00:23:44,760 --> 00:23:45,440
 to je legitimno

754
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:46,160
 i to je ispravno,

755
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:47,680
 ali evo danas smo ovdje

756
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:49,340
 da pokažemo pijetet

757
00:23:49,340 --> 00:23:50,260
 prema svim ljudima

758
00:23:50,260 --> 00:23:51,080
 koji su ubijeni

759
00:23:51,080 --> 00:23:52,100
 bez suđenja,

760
00:23:52,100 --> 00:23:53,500
 bez dokaza da si kriv.

761
00:23:53,500 --> 00:23:55,020
 Pa ko bi im šta skinuo

762
00:23:55,020 --> 00:23:55,560
 bi im kapu,

763
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:56,200
 daj im ruku

764
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:56,980
 i rekao,

765
00:23:56,980 --> 00:23:57,360
 to je to,

766
00:23:57,360 --> 00:23:58,680
 hrvatska ljevica je ozdravila,

767
00:23:59,100 --> 00:23:59,880
 možemo ići zajedno

768
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:00,980
 i neke priče o ovoj,

769
00:24:00,980 --> 00:24:01,680
 oni su zadojeni

770
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:02,520
 Jugoslovenski nacionalism.

771
00:24:02,520 --> 00:24:03,520
 Od centra desno.

772
00:24:03,520 --> 00:24:04,360
 Od centra desno,

773
00:24:04,360 --> 00:24:04,800
 samo to.

774
00:24:04,800 --> 00:24:05,960
 Pratit ćemo izbore

775
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:06,640
 i u mostu,

776
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:07,620
 a mi se vidimo

777
00:24:07,620 --> 00:24:08,000
 u ovoj,

778
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:09,060
 u ovoj saborskoj sezoni.

779
00:24:09,060 --> 00:24:09,420
 Hvala vam.

780
00:24:09,420 --> 00:24:10,240
 Hvala na gostovanje.

